params.sqlcmd: "select " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" as \\"PROC_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NO\\") as \\"PROC_NO\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NAME\\" as \\"PROC_NAME\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"WS_CD\\" as \\"WS_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" as \\"COMPANY_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"FIXED_LT\\") as \\"FIXED_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROP_LT\\") as \\"PROP_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"SAFETY_LT\\") as \\"SAFETY_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"SPOIL\\", 'FM99990.0999') as \\"SPOIL\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" as \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\" as \\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"STANDARD_COST\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"STANDARD_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\") as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_WS.\\"WS_NAME\\" as \\"WS_NAME\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_NAME\\" as \\"VEND_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_PROC_GRP, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_WS, " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"where " +" M_PROC_GRP.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD " +" and M_PROC_GRP.WS_CD = M_WS.WS_CD(+) " +" and M_PROC_GRP.VEND_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_CD(+) " +" and M_PROC_GRP.COMPANY_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD(+) " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +"order by " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NO\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\""

"insert into " +" M_PROC_GRP(\\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"PROC_CD\\", \\"PROC_NO\\", \\"PROC_NAME\\", \\"WS_CD\\", \\"COMPANY_CD\\", \\"VEND_CD\\", \\"FIXED_LT\\", \\"PROP_LT\\", \\"SAFETY_LT\\", \\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", \\"SPOIL\\", \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\", \\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\", \\"STANDARD_COST\\") " +"values " +" (?, ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?), ?, ?, ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), TO_NUMBER(?), ?, ?, TO_NUMBER(?))"

"update " +" M_PROC_GRP " +"set " +" \\"PROC_NO\\" = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" \\"PROC_NAME\\" = ?, " +" \\"WS_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"VEND_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"FIXED_LT\\" = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" \\"PROP_LT\\" = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" \\"SAFETY_LT\\" = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" \\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\" = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" \\"SPOIL\\" = TO_NUMBER(?), " +" \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" = ?, " +" \\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\" = ?, " +" \\"STANDARD_COST\\" = TO_NUMBER(?) " +"where " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"DRAW_CD\\" as \\"DRAW_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"SPEC\\" as \\"SPEC\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" as \\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" as \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"OPR_RSLT_TYP\\" as \\"OPR_RSLT_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"FIXED_LT\\" as \\"FIXED_LT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"PROP_LT\\" as \\"PROP_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_ITEM.\\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ISSUE_LT\\" as \\"ISSUE_LT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"SAFETY_LT\\" as \\"SAFETY_LT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\" as \\"UNIT_QTY_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" as \\"STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"MANHOUR_TYP\\" as \\"MANHOUR_TYP\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" as \\"PROC_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_PROC_GRP " +"where " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" as \\"COMPANY_CD\\" " +"from " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"where " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY.\\"CTRL_CD\\" = 'SYSTEM'"
"select " +" M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" as \\"WS_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_WS " +"where " +" M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_VEND_CTRL, " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"where " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD = SYS_MY_COMPANY.COMPANY_CD " +" and SYS_MY_COMPANY.CTRL_CD = 'SYSTEM' " +""
"delete from " +" M_PROC_GRP " +"where " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"
"delete from " +" M_PROC_GRP " +"where " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"
"delete from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"
"delete from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"
"delete from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ?"
"delete from " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H " +"where " +" M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_SBCNT_UNIT_COST_H.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" as \\"WS_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_WS " +"where " +" M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_WS.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" as \\"PROC_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NO\\" as \\"PROC_NO\\" " +"from " +" M_PROC_GRP " +"where " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NO\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_PROC_GRP " +"where " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ? " +"FOR UPDATE nowait"

"select " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" as \\"PROC_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NO\\") as \\"PROC_NO\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NAME\\" as \\"PROC_NAME\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"WS_CD\\" as \\"WS_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" as \\"COMPANY_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"FIXED_LT\\") as \\"FIXED_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROP_LT\\") as \\"PROP_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"SAFETY_LT\\") as \\"SAFETY_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"SPOIL\\", 'FM99990.0999') as \\"SPOIL\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" as \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\" as \\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"STANDARD_COST\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"STANDARD_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\") as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_WS.\\"WS_NAME\\" as \\"WS_NAME\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_NAME\\" as \\"VEND_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_PROC_GRP, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_WS, " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"where " +" M_PROC_GRP.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD " +" and M_PROC_GRP.WS_CD = M_WS.WS_CD(+) " +" and M_PROC_GRP.VEND_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_CD(+) " +" and M_PROC_GRP.COMPANY_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD(+) " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +"order by " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NO\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" " +"for update nowait"

"select " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" as \\"PROC_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NO\\") as \\"PROC_NO\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NAME\\" as \\"PROC_NAME\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"WS_CD\\" as \\"WS_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" as \\"COMPANY_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"FIXED_LT\\") as \\"FIXED_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROP_LT\\") as \\"PROP_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"SAFETY_LT\\") as \\"SAFETY_LT\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"SPOIL\\", 'FM99990.0999') as \\"SPOIL\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" as \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\" as \\"ACPT_INSPC_TYP\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"STANDARD_COST\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"STANDARD_COST\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_PROC_GRP.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\") as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_WS.\\"WS_NAME\\" as \\"WS_NAME\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_NAME\\" as \\"VEND_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_PROC_GRP, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_WS, " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"where " +" M_PROC_GRP.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD " +" and M_PROC_GRP.WS_CD = M_WS.WS_CD(+) " +" and M_PROC_GRP.VEND_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.VEND_CD(+) " +" and M_PROC_GRP.COMPANY_CD = M_VEND_CTRL.COMPANY_CD(+) " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" = ? " +"order by " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NO\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" " +"for update nowait"
"SELECT " +" PARA.VALUE " +"FROM " +" SYS_PARAMETER PARA " +"WHERE " +" PARA.NAME = 'TIME_CTRL'"

"SELECT " +" VALUE.DISPLAY_NAME " +"FROM " +" SYS_TYPE_VALUE VALUE, " +" SYS_PARAMETER PARA " +"WHERE " +" VALUE.NAME = 'PROC_GRP_LT_UNIT' " +" AND VALUE.VALUE = PARA.VALUE " +" AND PARA.NAME = 'PROC_GRP_LT_UNIT'"

"SELECT " +" BOM.ITEM_CD AS ITEM_CD, " +" BOM.FIXED_LT AS FIXED_LT " +"FROM " +" M_ASP_BOM BOM " +"WHERE " +" BOM.ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND BOM.PROC_NO = 10 " +" AND BOM.PROC_CD = '10' " +" AND BOM.INSTRUCTION_TYP = 'U' " +" AND BOM.INSTRUCTION_CD = 'M'"
